elements.expression: CASE  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('am', 'ac','om') THEN 'Livre imprim√©'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='as' THEN 'Revue imprim√©e'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN('gm','gn','gs') THEN 'DVD'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='bm' THEN 'Manuscrit'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('jm', 'im' ,'jn') THEN 'CD'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='km' THEN 'Image fixe'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='em' THEN 'Carte imprim√©e'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='cm' THEN 'Partition imprim√©e'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('mm','ms') THEN 'Document multimedia multisupport'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='lm' THEN 'Document √©lectronique'  ELSE 'Autre document' END
